    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in as-is condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dents, areas of surface rust, and heavily faded clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and the headliner is beginning to sag. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent check engine light and a noticeable transmission slip between gears. The brakes and tires are also near the end of their service life. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical skills or a source for parts, but it is not currently recommended for daily commuting without major repairs.",
      "price": 4800.0,
