    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks and drives great. It's ready to hit the road for its next big adventure! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself how smooth it feels.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the legendary S65 4.0L V8 engine featuring independent throttle bodies and a 8,400 RPM redline. This example utilizes a lightning-fast 7-speed M Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) paired with a variable M Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, benefiting from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and precise rack-and-pinion steering feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the high-strung valvetrain remains reliable. Though it displays minor cosmetic patina expected of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the powertrain remains robust and the torque curve is as flat and predictable as ever.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
