    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine with only minor, age-appropriate blemishes that do not detract from its overall curb appeal. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats have been treated regularly, and all electronic features\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, it\u2019s in solid shape with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at regular intervals. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, ensuring it's ready for the road. It\u2019s a dependable, attractive choice for anyone seeking a high-quality driving experience.",
